Display the list of all defined relations and optionnally attributes in this entire wiki.

== Usage ==

{{{
<<ListRelations arguments>>
}}}

== Arguments ==

All [[Help:PageList|PageList]] arguments, plus the following one:

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **mode**
| "relations" or "attributes" or "all"
| relations
|}

